{"tid":326733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"那年那個巴士站","createTime":"2017-07-18T08:41:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-20T08:10:08.000Z","uid":113545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e47fb5704ceaf050aba4887bc9e63833fb30710b","tid":326733,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T08:41:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/nip8mr0t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fnip8mr0t&h=94ca15cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《那年那個巴士站》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n那個用水彩繪畫的灰白色的天空褪色了。大概是某君想用水洗刷一下天空，偶爾轉一轉顏色。洗刷過之後，一定會變得明亮清澈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可是洗刷掉的灰白色的污水，正正灑落在我們的頭上和身上。那時我撐著雨傘，送她來到這個巴士站。她遞上一張紙巾給全身濕透的我。對於雨水洗臉，我倒是不太介意的。正好掩藏著眼睛不由自主流下的情感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n她自我檢查一番，沒多濕，只是鞋子襪子無可避免的被水濺濕浸濕。確實，有些事情是無可避免的。包括雨水漫遊人間，時間逼迫人類。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n也許我對她了解太少，就如我不知道這巴士站的巴士，會駛到哪裡去。她掏出了那個不是我送的銀包，準備好八達通。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「你回去吧，車快到了，不用送。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「反正都是最後一次送你，就讓我等一下吧。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「不，你已經等得夠多了。再等下去也不會改變什麼。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我收起雨傘，工整地將雨傘收卷好，然後遞給她。她一臉迷茫，徐徐接過雨傘。雨傘流下的雨水落在地上，再分不出哪些雨水曾帶著我的希望。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「好了，車來了，再見。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完<br />\n<br />\n那年那間便利店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/310795/page/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/310795/page/1?ref=android</a>"},{"pid":"823dd270ded55e480b86273fd676010c7301d604","tid":326733,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:09:24.000Z","msg":"好大雨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfb9a2e89c6fef9529c78872a44cc154f839d472","tid":326733,"uid":70088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T12:14:25.000Z","msg":"不，你已經等得夠多了。再等下去也不會改變什麼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa522131c1b17e9043ae06f61ccb5424a368ecfa","tid":326733,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T16:32:48.000Z","msg":"到底等幾耐，先算係夠多呢？<br />\n我望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f881dfbc8a7e4960583cf3f885c1552e6a3e4439","tid":326733,"uid":70088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T17:17:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>到底等幾耐，先算係夠多呢？<br />\n我望唔透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當有一日你番番去同一個地方<br />\n諗番起同一個人<br />\n但你已經變左既時候<br />\n<br />\n你就知道你唔洗再等<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n共勉之<br />\n朋友"},{"pid":"eadf77d94f409967ba18ea25a95842d7b3942351","tid":326733,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T08:24:03.000Z","msg":"有時令人依戀的<br />\n並不是結果<br />\n而是等待的過程<br />\n<br />\n自虐的愛情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45465f66322d4e78dfdde941f6ca34558d2d1aab","tid":326733,"uid":70088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:24:38.000Z","msg":"也許那種痛已經習慣到像毒癮一樣"},{"pid":"01a98071e594acae530e1827b1f1dd6dbd764fa9","tid":326733,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T13:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a0a3240755e09527bf8c4f938e38b9211ebf93","tid":326733,"uid":113545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T08:10:08.000Z","msg":"有時睇到佢ig近況<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n望住佢張相<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}